name: Planet of the apes new kingdom
author: Wes Ball
description: Many years after the reign of Caesar, a young ape goes on a journey that will lead him to question everything he's been taught about the past and make choices that will define a future for apes and humans

name: The astronaut
author: Adam Sandler
description: After six months on a lonely space mission, an astronaut confronts the problems in his marriage with the help of the mysterious stowaway he finds on his ship.
